<td id="title_text"><h1><a title="Band Printer" class="currentChild" href="Band_Printer">Band Printer</a></h1></td>



</tr></table>
</td>
</tr></table></div>



<div id="content" class="content wikipage" lang="en" dir="ltr">
<p id="l1">
A type of <a title="Impact Printer" href="Impact_Printer">impact printer</a> which contains a metal <a title="Band" href="Band">band</a> with character shapes imprinted on it. During output, the band rotates horizontally past the paper, and a hammer strikes the band opposite the appropriate character, pressing it through an inked ribbon and onto the paper. Band printers can print from 300 to 2000 lines per minute. Also known as a <a title="Belt Printer" href="http://printwiki.org/Belt_Printer">belt printer</a>. 
</p>
